  "text": "The examples of collaborating with partners to employ staff and addressing staff needs to improve retention demonstrate the managers in both organisations were effectively using their available \"decision space\"-in some cases informal [CITATION_1] -to adjust to the changing context. This was easier for Lacor hospital being a smaller institution which has integrated functions for recruitment, deployment and funding of posts, has the autonomy to make rapid changes and has strong links to training institutions to support their recruitment processes.",
